                                     {
                                         "text":  "### Location\n\nAfter studying what the data shows us about the formation of the universe, stars, and planets, we can begin to talk about the regions of our planet.\n\nBut to do this, we must know how to locate ourselves on it.",
                                         "source":  [

                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "markdown",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection: Where am I?</b><br /><br />How do you locate yourself on planet Earth?</div></div></center></p>",
                                         "source":  [

                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "html",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "There are many answers to this reflection.\n\nIf your answer was “using maps, my phone, street names,” they are all correct—but there is something more we can explore. And that is exactly what we will begin to do in the upcoming texts of the *Atlas*.",
                                         "source":  [

                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "markdown",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     }
